<h3><i class="fa fa-cogs"></i> Settings</h3>
<p>This is the <strong>Settings</strong> tab content.</p>
<p>You could place custom forms or configuration options here that are specific to your tool's operation.</p>
<p>Unlike the main plugin configuration, which uses blueprints, this content is rendered via a Twig template, giving you full control over the markup and logic.</p>
